In 2023, EBIT of the Mercedes-Benz Mobility segment 
amounted to €1,302 million (2022: €2,428 million); 
adjusted EBIT was €1,695 million (2022: €2,428 million).

The CMS encompasses seven 
elements that build on one another: Compliance Val-
ues; Compliance Targets; Compliance Organization; 
Compliance Risks; Compliance Programme; Training; 
and Monitoring and Improvement.
